        <div class="how-tree" data-a data-d="1">
          <div class="how-tree-header">
            <span class="tree-dot tree-dot-1"></span>
            <span class="tree-dot tree-dot-2"></span>
            <span class="tree-dot tree-dot-3"></span>
          </div>
<pre>your-workspace/
├── <span class="hl">a-society/</span>          <span class="dim">← the framework</span>
│   ├── <span class="hl">general/</span>        <span class="note">reusable templates</span>
│   ├── <span class="hl">runtime/</span>        <span class="note">executable layer</span>
│   └── <span class="hl">a-docs/</span>         <span class="note">a-society's own docs</span>
│
└── <span class="hl">my-project/</span>         <span class="dim">← your project</span>
    ├── [project files]
    └── <span class="hl">a-docs/</span>         <span class="note">initialized by runtime</span>
        ├── agents.md
        ├── roles/
        ├── indexes/
        └── workflow/</pre>
        </div>
        <div class="how-steps" data-a data-d="2">
          <div class="how-step">
            <div class="how-step-num">1</div>
            <div class="how-step-content">
              <h4>Clone the framework</h4>
              <p>Place <code>a-society/</code> in a workspace folder alongside your project. It never modifies your project files.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="how-step">
            <div class="how-step-num">2</div>
            <div class="how-step-content">
              <h4>Start the runtime</h4>
              <p>The runtime provides a local web server and browser UI at <code>localhost:3000</code>. No cloud required.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="how-step">
            <div class="how-step-num">3</div>
            <div class="how-step-content">
              <h4>Configure your model</h4>
              <p>Set your LLM provider, API key, and model ID in Settings. Works with Anthropic, OpenAI, and compatible APIs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="how-step">
            <div class="how-step-num">4</div>
            <div class="how-step-content">
              <h4>Initialize your project</h4>
              <p>The runtime scaffolds the compulsory <code>a-docs/</code> surfaces and runs an Owner-led initialization flow to fill them with project truth.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="how-step">
            <div class="how-step-num">5</div>
            <div class="how-step-content">
              <h4>Work through roles and workflows</h4>
              <p>Every new flow is routed through the designed workflow. Agents receive structured context, act through explicit roles, and leave records.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

